t: "Nabiyow keenik ixxic:sin yallittey isin taqbudeenik faxe ginooy takkay gino suge waytik qimbissah gintam teetik tanii wohuk lakal woo gino qiddiiy sarra tet uynuwwuwy is elle sugte innah tet gacissam tanii?usun wohul tugacsaanam maduudaanak Nabiyow keenik ixxic:Yalla kinni gino suge waytik gintaah tohuk lakal tet qiddaah sarra tet taynuwweeh gacissam, tokkel isin cakki gitak deedal gitâ fanah mannal daggawtaanaah"